Internal testing build of BudgeTrak v2.10.00.
- Fix: full backup restore now refreshes the UI immediately. Previously categories, recurring expenses, and income sources could appear empty/default until the app was force-stopped and reopened.
- Restore dialog: auto-opens the folder picker, remembers your backup folder for future restores, and rejects invalid picks (wrong folder or no backup files).
- Internal testing only: this build defaults all users to Subscriber tier so testers can exercise paid features without a billing flow. Will switch to Google Play billing in a future build.
